g.title: create_shapefile_dir
g.text: create a direcorty for downloading the shapefiles for the study region.

g.title: download_shapefile_archive
g.text: download the zip file of the region which contains the boundary, tracts, metadata.xml and nps_tracts.xml files.

g.title: uncompress_shapefile
g.text: create a directory as the archive filename and extract the files.

g.title: read_shapefile
g.text: read the shapefile for the region and save it as a spatial vector object.

g.title: get_treepolygon
g.text: Get Tree-ring data from the ITRDB for tree_buffer around GRCA

g.title: extract_tree_ring_data
g.text: get all the tree ring chronologies and extract the values for the study region.
